  "detailed_description": "<strong>Pop Journey  </strong><br>starting point of the game is loveliness and peace. Enjoy peace of mind while playing.<br><br><strong>Ever changing Meidu</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140840/extras/00fb1bfe21e4de2006527b82e2fd93ae.poster.avif?t=1768862161\" width=640 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140840/extras/00fb1bfe21e4de2006527b82e2fd93ae.webm?t=1768862161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140840/extras/00fb1bfe21e4de2006527b82e2fd93ae.mp4?t=1768862161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>View outside the window</strong><br>Looking at the scenery outside the window calms the upset mood<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140840/extras/2eba912e6a83ecb9d9a2e5f6c56997f4.poster.avif?t=1768862161\" width=640 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140840/extras/2eba912e6a83ecb9d9a2e5f6c56997f4.webm?t=1768862161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140840/extras/2eba912e6a83ecb9d9a2e5f6c56997f4.mp4?t=1768862161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong><br>Pop Journey is a level-based puzzle game, where you need to complete the goals of each level to progress within the game.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tap two or more cubes of the same color to blast them and help complete the goals.<br></li><li>Combine a number of cubes to create powerful boosters such as the rocket, bomb and color bomb to clear the obstacles and reach the level goal.<br></li><li>You can also combine these boosters for bigger combos and blast your way to success!<br></li><li>You have a limited number of moves for each level, so plan each move accordingly.</li></ul><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Enjoy the scenery of the journey<br></li><li>Help Meidu change clothes<br></li><li>Challenging match-3 game<br></li><li>Find the gold coins hidden in the carriage</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Pop Journey  </strong><br>starting point of the game is loveliness and peace. Enjoy peace of mind while playing.<br><br><strong>Ever changing Meidu</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140840/extras/00fb1bfe21e4de2006527b82e2fd93ae.poster.avif?t=1768862161\" width=640 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140840/extras/00fb1bfe21e4de2006527b82e2fd93ae.webm?t=1768862161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140840/extras/00fb1bfe21e4de2006527b82e2fd93ae.mp4?t=1768862161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>View outside the window</strong><br>Looking at the scenery outside the window calms the upset mood<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140840/extras/2eba912e6a83ecb9d9a2e5f6c56997f4.poster.avif?t=1768862161\" width=640 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140840/extras/2eba912e6a83ecb9d9a2e5f6c56997f4.webm?t=1768862161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140840/extras/2eba912e6a83ecb9d9a2e5f6c56997f4.mp4?t=1768862161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong><br>Pop Journey is a level-based puzzle game, where you need to complete the goals of each level to progress within the game.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tap two or more cubes of the same color to blast them and help complete the goals.<br></li><li>Combine a number of cubes to create powerful boosters such as the rocket, bomb and color bomb to clear the obstacles and reach the level goal.<br></li><li>You can also combine these boosters for bigger combos and blast your way to success!<br></li><li>You have a limited number of moves for each level, so plan each move accordingly.</li></ul><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Enjoy the scenery of the journey<br></li><li>Help Meidu change clothes<br></li><li>Challenging match-3 game<br></li><li>Find the gold coins hidden in the carriage</li></ul>",
